Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer! It's the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, ma'am, we're counting on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you and Yui to guide\Nand drive us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you have quite a bit\Nof time on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fixtures of Summer"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that we brought you\Nout on your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Narumi, you're a police officer\Nin the traffic safety division, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Leave all\Nthe traffic laws to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he passed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, traffic safety division?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She goes out of control when\Nshe's behind the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll have Kagami and Tsukasa\Nbe our human sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... Unusual\Nfor a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotten separated\Nfrom the other car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ma'am, you went\Nonto the wrong road!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's a one-way street!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known better!\NBoth of them were the wrong pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah yeah... Yo yo yo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:47.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gravity... Gravity...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feel the power {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That car is amazing!\NWho's driving it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The braking drift on\Nthe way down is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A FD car is losing in the plunge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got some serious pickup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing!\NIt barely missed the guardrail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The point of attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the five consecutive\Nhairpin curves up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't feel the difference\Nin love, go for a future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your eyes, open your mind,\Nfeel the power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going in too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the brakes die or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"GRINNNND"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"GRINNNND"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this _________-D-like\Nway of driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nanako... You're a good driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I always get motion\Nsickness when I ride in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I brought some medicine\Nto prevent motion sickness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with your driving, Miss Nanako,\NI didn't get sick at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can't afford to comment\Nabout that in this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Keep the beach clean"\N"FIREWORKS ARE FORBIDDEN"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll look for a place to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sunny out, it's the perfect day\Nto go swim in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... I wondered what\Nwould happen to us yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put my\Nbathing suit on before we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata-{\i1}san{\i0}, are you\Nserious about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I don't think I've\Nheard of anyone your age
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wearing their school swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagamin, there are needs\Nfor such things as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sixth grade, class 3" "Izumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is that bathing suit from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've got good\Nathletic skills to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have one of\Nthose inflatable tubes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I can swim\Ndoesn't mean that I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,plunge through the waters\Nswimming freestyle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling I have is that of leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-E-l-S-U-R-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, add to that the need for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,visually speaking, I can't do without\Nthe school swimsuit and tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people with those needs don't\Neven come to the beach, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In manga and anime, splitting\Nwatermelons is a standard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't see it that often\Nin real life, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe it's because\Nit feels like it's a waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. When you destroy\Na watermelon with a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you end up with watermelon\Nall over your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been watching\Ntoo much anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done it before, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nsince you're rich and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have to say I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nthe image is such that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rich are even less likely\Nto have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it all along, but things\Njust don't end up like in manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I couldn't\Nmeet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, it's you-know-what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us loners really have it lonely,\Nhaving to come to the beach with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an all-girls group at our age\Nto chaperone, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, you have it wron--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you were to compromise\Nand tote something like him along,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think you're just fine\Nwith an all-girls group?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm telling you--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More and more people are\Ngetting married later in life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we don't have to rush,\Nand can just go really slowly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have time only because my husband\Nand I have a commuter marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually married!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is a mecca\Nfor picking up girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we sure have nothing going for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's good, because\Nwe're not being annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we have\Nsomeone like this with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe they all think we're\Njust sisters on a family vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ice"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go, Shouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's kinda gross to sit down\Nwhen you're still sopping wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Tsukasa, you'll beat it\Nwith the "air chair" pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My neck's all tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just like what I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we've been served something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's a picture-perfect model\Nof the beach house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Curry with no solid contents!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from a beach house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Even if you\Nwouldn't eat it normally,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems really tasty when\Nyou eat it in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beer at the beach is the best after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once in a while, you get\Na really lukewarm one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's absurd that a hot dog\Nwould cost 300 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. And it's\Npractically raw, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't mind,\Nand you still eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I kinda like how
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the chicken is oily and has\Ntoo much spice on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very plain fried noodles like this\Nare rather tasty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you take it with you and\Neat it back at home, it tastes awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I guess that's what \Nmakes it the beach house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:12.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Konata, thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really tasty enough\Nto make that much fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as good as running along the\Nbeach with nothing but a loincloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that another reference\Nto some anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ice"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it...\NLet's stay another night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, what about your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still on paid vacation tomorrow,\Nso I'm fine, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're exaggerating, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does your hair feel so creaky\Nafter you swim in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Maybe it has something\Nto do with the salt or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Most of it is caused\Nby the salt and ultraviolet light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, your hair is always\Nexposed to ultraviolet light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, explaining in detail\Nwill take a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why your hair\Ngets damaged at the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is because your hair is exposed\Nto strong rays of ultraviolet light
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after it loses moisture from the salt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is in seawater,\Nas well as the ocean breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, if you bask in\Nstrong ultraviolet rays outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the melanin pigments start to mutate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it causes your hair\Nto turn a bit brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the salt, or other impurities\Nsuch as chlorine,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are allowed to remain in your hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this causes your hair to be\Nbrittle or brown as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reasons why your hair gets\Ndamaged especially in the summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are because of ultraviolet rays\Nand deposits of impurities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are caused by cuticles that\Nare damaged by such conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When hit by strong ultraviolet light,\Nthe cystine bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that preserve your hair's\Nnatural strength get severed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei, Timotei, Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how other people see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our conversations don't last long...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to say we look like family,\Nor at least relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to run with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei, Timotei, Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the memories! I used to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!\NThis is the reaction that I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the old man gags.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a flag up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the event starts up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, so that you can see both\Nchoices in the end, save often!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tossing a rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've completed the image gallery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you being like that is\Nexactly why, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about guys hitting on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it up originally anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't thought of such a thing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanted someone\Nto hit on you, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I missed seeing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about\Nwhat you do with unwanted hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty smooth all around,\Nso I don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm, well, normal, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually today was rather dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, it was almost time\Nfor you-know-what...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you-know-what.\NI see, then that was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were okay, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it totally missed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it ended last week,\NI thought that I had perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a problem when it\Nstarts up at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad when you're the only one\Nthat can't go into the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but on the other hand,\Nto use that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right, you get\Nhesitant or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never used one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a blunt conversation\Nyou two are having.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that this was something\Nthat really happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who works at a certain\Nvideo software wholesaler
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finished work for that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got on a bus late at night\Nlike he usually does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His house was towards\Nthe end of the bus route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, as he was riding the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,other passengers started\Nleaving one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:14:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he ended up as\Nthe only passenger left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The driver mistakenly thought that\Nthere was nobody left on the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He started to sing, in a loud voice,\N{\i1}Danzen! Futari wa ______ Cure{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the rumor that I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it really was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad! I was really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sukekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you bring that mask from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Inugami Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is worth scaring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say something that funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukasa... I'm Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It was so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's the moment where a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,took one more step towards\Nbecoming an adult, Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Comp-Fest seems\Nto be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese people are suckers\Nfor the words "limited edition."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that one phrase makes\Nthe difference in sales,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they should just do it every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they did, then it wouldn't be\Nappreciated as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, make sure to clean\Nyour rooms during vacation, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these bring back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are textbooks\NI used in junior high!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, look! Look at this album!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Dad like totally\Nawful in this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing of Dad was\Nreally on my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be having fun, but\Nhow's the cleaning part coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you want these clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll leave these here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is she using me as her\Ntrash bin or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but to start flipping\Nthrough albums and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that delays things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know how that feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you find an old magazine,\Nyou can't help but read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't throw much stuff away,\Nso it always takes her longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still at it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Tsukasa seems to be\Nthe type that keeps everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, Kagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you look like the type that\Nthrows everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, why is your image\Nof me so aggressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you had kept your\Njunior high textbooks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left all that stuff behind at school,\Nwith my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, take them home.\NDon't cause trouble for the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally done cleaning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I think I'll never\Nuse some things again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered the times\Nthat I had used them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't bring myself\Nto throw them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, there are people that want\Nto keep anything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you're the typical case\Nof someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, on the other hand, might even\Nthrow away something that you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you leave behind your\Ntextbooks and stuff already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, you should get your teeth\Ntreated before school starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but it's just not\Nsomething I deal with well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you don't like it that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry about making you\Nhead over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't go over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have the dentist\Ncome here as a house call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes so quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that {\i1}Lucky Channel {\i0}is\Nalready on its sixth episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Akira Kogami, who has the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd like to say people are getting\Nused to this segment too" syndrome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyaru-n!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, my assistant,\NMinoru Shiraishi-{\i1}kun{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:12.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Scared... I'm so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--is still not used to this \Nyet. He looks really nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's like, he's fretting \Nover everyone looking at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tell me, what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I went to the mountains because \NAkira-{\i1}sama {\i0}told me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'd really like him to get \Nused to his job quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right, I also went to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Especially how he should watch \Nhis speech towards his superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:22.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm doing everything I can \Nto make this show funny too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How many times do I have to \Ntell him before he understands?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right... The gum was really \Ntough... 54 pieces of gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Honestly, it's getting irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now today, we'd like to introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I put 54 pieces of gum in my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--one of the key characters in \N{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}, Konata Izumi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's how I'm doing my best, I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--What more do I need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm so troubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Konata Izumi-{\i1}san\N{\i0}is 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her hobbies are games, anime,\Nand reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, according to\Nthe source material,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she always checks out\Nthe new shows and new books,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and spends all weekend storming\Nthrough 'net games until dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, an otaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta think of something fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otaku are, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in their house all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:20:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people that cry watching\N{\i1}The Dog of Flanders {\i0}and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dated can your image\Nof an otaku be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been doing your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go saying random stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that both\N{\i1}The Dog of Flanders{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cute {\i1}moe {\i0}characters both\Nhave a healing effect, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But girls like me are\Nmuch better than dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're seeking really pretty\Nand cute maidens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look to the right,\Nthey look to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look to left, they look left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they're in line\Nall night for a concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they can't take baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They end up with\Nhorrible smell problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, they want to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that one thought drives them\Ninto the damned heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,burning in the infernal sun as\Nthey wait for me to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the bandannas\Nthey wrap around their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get so wet that you can\Nwring sweat out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they are customers, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they don't let me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finish a conversation quickly\Nduring a handshake session,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or if they make some off-topic\Ncomment during my MC,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you kinda get sympathetic, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like... "Oh, I'm here now\Nbecause of all these people."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to do my best\Nfor these people."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's what it's like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know in due time\Njust how hard it is to be an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you've seen both\Nthe sweet and the sour side of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's when the real taste comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a fan or a client\Nthat you can't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, did you get an idea\Nof Konata-{\i1}san{\i0}'s character?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I hope to see you again\Nin the next {\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, instead of\Nintroducing Konata,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was more of introducing otaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, the reporter saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Kage is the best after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tsukasa, did you\Nput something in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s singing voice\Nwill be fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can sing it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miyuki, what are you\Ngoing to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know that many songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm a bit embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what you're going with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:16.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Tomorrow is special, a special day ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:20.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The one chance you get a year ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:24.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Oh darling ♪\NL-O-V-E, lovely, Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:27.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Oh darling, I love you ♪\NL-O-V-E, lovely, Sayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Sayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:31.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Everyone is worked up in the carnival ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:34.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Capture his heart to be yours ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Oh baby ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name isn't Sayuri Kuninama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Oh, baby, love me do ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you, who is Sayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her membership number?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:46.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A sweet, sweet chocolate of love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:50.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Even if I tried giving it to you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:53.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I won't stand out at all ♪\NYou're being too noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:57.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ So I'm going to settle it\Nusing my last resort ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:00.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Valentine's Day kiss ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:04.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Valentine's Day kiss ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Valentine's Day kiss ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:11.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Wrapped with a ribbon ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the\Nnext episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when you want\Nto get rid of that hangnail
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pull on it, only to have it peel off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,much deeper than you expected,\Nleaving you in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and the timing to\Nscratch off that scab...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it gets itchy and you think\Nyou want to get it off soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you start peeling it off\Nslowly from the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you think it's all right\Nand rip off the center part,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you end up bleeding after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That also gives\Na pretty damaging blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Image.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:43.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Image"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
